<div>
<pre class="mermaid mermaid-js">flowchart TD
  A[Start] --&gt; B[Create tools dir]
  B --&gt; C[Set env vars]
  C --&gt; D[Download oc client]
  D --&gt; E[Install oc &amp; kubectl]
  E --&gt; F[Download openshift-install]
  F --&gt; G[Install openshift-install binary]
  G --&gt; H[Generate SSH key &amp; add to agent]
  H --&gt; I[Write install-config.yaml]
  I --&gt; J[Run openshift-install create cluster]
  J --&gt; K[Wait for cluster readiness]
  K --&gt; L[Done]
